##################################################################################
# OTPHP
# An object-oriented one-time password (OTP) authentication library written in PHP
##################################################################################

Testing
=======

OTPHP comes with two PHPUnit unit tests to validate functionality of the OTPServer and the ClientEntity.

To run these tests:

1. Install PHPUnit
2. Install OTPHP via the installation script
3. Copy the two tests into the root directory of the OTPHP installation
4. Run the tests from the command line using the phpunit command


